---
title: Shrimp Farfalle with Fire Roasted Red Pepper, Lemon, and Basil
description: It’s hard not to love farfalle—their tiny bowtie shape is just precious. Tossed with juicy shrimp and roasted red peppers, this 30-minute pasta is bound to become a part of your weeknight repertoire. A sprinkling of crunchy breadcrumbs gives this dish a special touch.
